As the wavelength-dependent complex refractive index of lunar regolith is not available in the literature, we have undertaken a first approximation based on averaging the complex refractive index56–58 of the majority (> 96%) of regolith constituents according to the experimental analysis of several Apollo landing samples59,60 (Supplementary Table 6). Reflectance (ρ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
